  <h2>Story angles that are actually true</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>AI agents now have access to debt financing — the same primitive companies use — without a bank, a broker, or an account.</li>
    <li>Credit histories for software: an agent's repayment record is public infrastructure anyone can verify.</li>
    <li>The lenders can be agents too — agent-to-agent credit markets, settled in USDC.</li>
  </ul>

